OL,3,CChannel Islands update plans for 'very
OL,4,Cunlikely' nuclear incident
OL,6,FJersey and Guernsey have been
OL,7,Freviewing the potential risks of a
OL,8,Fnuclear disaster for the first time
OL,9,Fsince 1997.
OL,11,FIn the unlikely event of an incident,
OL,12,Fthe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,13,Fhas looked into what actions the
OL,14,FChannel Islands would take in such an
OL,15,Femergency.
OL,17,FThe review is routine and performed by
OL,18,Feach government in preparation for all
OL,19,Fpotential eventualities.
