OL,3,CChannel Islands update plans for 'very
OL,4,Cunlikely' nuclear incident
OL,6,FJersey and Guernsey's Radiation
OL,7,FAdvisory Group, which is made up of
OL,8,Fclinicians and scientists from both
OL,9,Fislands, discussed whether they should
OL,10,Fstockpile iodine and unanimously
OL,11,Frecommended against it.
OL,13,FThe advice was instead to focus on
OL,14,Fseeking shelter in the very unlikely
OL,15,Fscenario of a nuclear incident.
OL,17,FDr Nicola Brink, Guernsey's Director
OL,18,Fof Public Health, says: "This review
OL,19,Fwas commissioned as part of our normal
OL,20,Fcycle of risk assessment as we haven't
OL,21,Flooked at this issue since 1997.
