OL,3,CChannel Islands update plans for 'very
OL,4,Cunlikely' nuclear incident
OL,6,F"This is part of our on-going plan to
OL,7,Fupdate and review a number of Public
OL,8,FHealth risks. The report was
OL,9,Freassuring in that it confirmed that
OL,10,Fthe risk of such an incident occurring
OL,11,Fis very small.
OL,13,F"The authors examined worst-case
OL,14,Fscenarios, which is important context,
OL,15,Fand even in the very unlikely event
OL,16,Fsuch an incident occurred, our normal
OL,17,Fweather patterns would likely result
OL,18,Fin minimal risk to public health.
