OL,3,CChannel Islands update plans for 'very
OL,4,Cunlikely' nuclear incident
OL,6,F"Our emergency plans are being updated
OL,7,Ffollowing the review but the key
OL,8,Fpublic health advice would, should
OL,9,Fsuch an unlikely event occur, be for
OL,10,Fthe community to seek shelter as a
OL,11,Fpriority."
